' —(1) Subject to subsections (3) and (4) below, the Secretary of State may, by order made by statutory instrument, amend —


(a) the categories of shop exempt from the provisions of this Act under section 2 above;

(b) Schedule 2 to this Act (which relates to the categories of shop entitled to Class A registration);

(c) the classes of shop entitled to be registered under subsection (5) of section 3 above; and

(d) subsection (5) of section 3 above by substituting for the words "two hours", such longer period, not exceeding six hours as the Secretary of State may specify.
